+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0191L6hMronXcMeFnTtK5Cdn","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Phase 11: Middleware Pipeline\n     2→\n     3→Add a middleware system that can intercept and transform tasks as they are processed.\n     4→\n     5→## Requirements\n     6→\n     7→- Middleware functions can be registered per queue.\n     8→- When a task is processed, it passes through all registered middleware in order before reaching the final handler.\n     9→- Each middleware receives the task and a \"next\" function. Calling \"next\" passes control to the next middleware (or the handler).\n    10→- If a middleware does NOT call \"next\", the task processing is skipped.\n    11→- Middleware can modify the task (e.g., adding metadata or transforming the payload).\n    12→- If a middleware throws an error, the task should be marked as failed.\n    13→- A processing function/handler can be registered per queue. It is invoked after all middleware have run.\n    14→- Each queue has its own independent middleware stack.\n    15→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d55f7efa-1a7c-4c18-baa6-46556b297090","uuid":"7d424249-ccbd-4d0b-9a5e-c8c605117d16","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/phases/phase-11.md","content":"# Phase 11: Middleware Pipeline\n\nAdd a middleware system that can intercept and transform tasks as they are processed.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Middleware functions can be registered per queue.\n- When a task is processed, it passes through all registered middleware in order before reaching the final handler.\n- Each middleware receives the task and a \"next\" function. Calling \"next\" passes control to the next middleware (or the handler).\n- If a middleware does NOT call \"next\", the task processing is skipped.\n- Middleware can modify the task (e.g., adding metadata or transforming the payload).\n- If a middleware throws an error, the task should be marked as failed.\n- A processing function/handler can be registered per queue. It is invoked after all middleware have run.\n- Each queue has its own independent middleware stack.\n","numLines":15,"startLine":1,"totalLines":15}}}
